## 📊 SQL Queries

### 1. Revenue by Item
```sql
SELECT 
    item_name,
    COUNT(*) AS total_orders,
    SUM(price) AS total_revenue,
    ROUND(
        SUM(price) / (SELECT SUM(price) FROM orders) * 100, 1
    ) AS revenue_pct
FROM orders
GROUP BY item_name
ORDER BY total_revenue DESC;
```
**Finding:** Top 3 items = 70%+ of total revenue

---

### 2. Hourly Demand — Iftar Spike
```sql
SELECT 
    HOUR(order_time) AS order_hour,
    COUNT(*) AS total_orders
FROM orders
GROUP BY HOUR(order_time)
ORDER BY total_orders DESC;
```
**Finding:** Clear 30-minute demand spike before iftar daily

---

### 3. Sehri vs Iftar Window
```sql
SELECT 
    CASE 
        WHEN HOUR(order_time) BETWEEN 3 AND 5 
            THEN 'Sehri Window'
        WHEN HOUR(order_time) BETWEEN 18 AND 20 
            THEN 'Iftar Window'
        ELSE 'Off-Peak'
    END AS time_window,
    COUNT(*) AS total_orders,
    SUM(price) AS total_revenue
FROM orders
GROUP BY time_window
ORDER BY total_orders DESC;
```
**Finding:** Iftar window had 3x more orders than sehri

